<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> nehst von Göczen
                                <expan>Visch<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er die zeit bey uns niht anheim
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> etc., also tun wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Göczen
                            <expan>Visch<ex>er</ex></expan> nu auf <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> schrift <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> zu
                        rede gesaczt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, er grabe und lass graben an dem
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        dewht ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>, daz er <add>daran</add>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> grübe <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> teͣt, denn
                        er <expan>pillich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sölt, spricht er, so mug ewr gnade die
                        gut wol <expan>fürwend<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> an söliche gericht, darinn sie
                                <expan>geleg<ex>en</ex></expan> sein. So well er das mit recht
                        daselbs <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
